    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J375">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Angle of a Landscape --</l>
                    <l>That every time I wake --</l>
                    <l>Between my Curtain and the Wall</l>
                    <l>Upon an ample Crack --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Like a Venetian -- waiting --</l>
                    <l>Accosts my open eye --</l>
                    <l>Is just a Bough of Apples --</l>
                    <l>Held slanting, in the Sky --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Pattern of a Chimney --</l>
                    <l>The Forehead of a Hill --</l>
                    <l>Sometimes -- a Vane's Forefinger --</l>
                    <l>But that's -- Occasional --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Seasons -- shift -- my Picture</l>
                    <l>Upon my Emerald Bough,</l>
                    <l>I wake -- to find no -- Emeralds --</l>
                    <l>Then -- Diamonds -- which the Snow</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>From Polar Caskets -- fetched me --</l>
                    <l>The Chimney -- and the Hill --</l>
                    <l>And just the Steeple's finger --</l>
                    <l>These -- never stir at all --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
